This paper deals with the problem of privacy-preserving prediction as a service, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses techniques for accelerating computation on encrypted data, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and computer engineering (cs.CE). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR, followed by cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SE, and cs.CE.
